  "title": "feat(community-widgets): add comprehensive test suite for color refinement list widget",
  "body": "## This PR has been superseded\r\n\r\nThis PR was created on the wrong repository. The color refinement list widget has its own dedicated repository.\r\n\r\n**✅ Correct PR Location:**  \r\nhttps://github.com/algolia/react-instantsearch-widget-color-refinement-list/pull/5\r\n\r\n### What happened\r\n- This PR was initially created on the InstantSearch monorepo\r\n- The widget actually lives in a separate repository: `algolia/react-instantsearch-widget-color-refinement-list`\r\n- Work has been moved to the correct repository (PR [#5](https://github.com/algolia/react-instantsearch-widget-color-refinement-list/pull/5))\r\n\r\n### Summary of Changes (now in correct repo)\r\n- Upgrade to React InstantSearch v7 (v2.0.0)\r\n- Comprehensive test suite (84 tests, ~85% coverage)\r\n- Migration guide and updated documentation\r\n- Centralised Algolia credentials configuration\r\n\r\nThis PR is **closed** and the branch has been deleted.  \r\nPlease review the work at the correct location: **[PR #5](https://github.com/algolia/react-instantsearch-widget-color-refinement-list/pull/5)** ☝️",
